00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,250
INT.

2
00:00:00,250 --> 00:00:03,000
COMMAND CENTER - NIGHT

将军 (General) paces, eyes on a map.

3
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:03,750
灯光 (Lights) flicker.

4
00:00:03,750 --> 00:00:04,500
心跳声 (Heartbeats) echo.

5
00:00:04,500 --> 00:00:07,500
将军: (into radio) 部队，准备行动。我们的时间到了。我们必须突破敌人的防线，夺回城市。每个人都要保持警惕，生死在此一搏。

无线电静默。镜头拉远，展现外面的战备景象，士兵们静待命令，夜空中星光与战火交织。

Translation:
General paces, eyes on a map.

6
00:00:07,500 --> 00:00:08,000
Lights flicker.

7
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:08,500
Heartbeats echo.

8
00:00:08,500 --> 00:00:10,000
General: (into radio) Troops, get ready.

9
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:11,000
Our time has come.

10
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:13,750
We must break through the enemy’s lines and reclaim the city.

11
00:00:13,750 --> 00:00:16,250
Everyone, stay alert; life and death hang in the balance.

12
00:00:16,250 --> 00:00:16,750
Radio silence.

13
00:00:16,750 --> 00:00:22,250
The camera pulls back, showing the preparation outside, soldiers awaiting orders, starlight mingling with the fires of war in the night sky.